{"tid":2372068,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［赴湯杜火案］律政司要求上訴庭釐清「共同犯罪原則」可否套用於暴動罪下週一審理","createTime":"2021-01-19T10:46:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T11:32:07.000Z","uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b5cb004f3c0b69ce8af62c280f7bc80244074724","tid":2372068,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T10:46:35.000Z","msg":"【資訊部獨家】去年七月裁定暴動罪名不成立的上環「赴湯杜火」案，律政司於去年9月15日，回歸後首次援引《刑事訴訟程序條例》第81D條向上訴庭尋求法律意見，要求釐清「共同犯罪原則」（joint enterprise）可否套用在公眾集會的控罪，包括非法集結及暴動。是次上訴不會影響原案三人的無罪裁決，但對日後同類案件有重大影響。<br />\n<br />\n根據司法機構網頁顯示，是次聆訊將由潘兆初高等法院首席法官，麥機智上訴庭副庭長及彭寶琴法官負責審理，案件將於1月25日進行上午10時進行聆訊，預計審期1日。<br />\n<br />\n#20210119新聞"},{"pid":"8eba8524ad9d5c60067b68bdcbe6b6eb5459addb","tid":2372068,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T10:55:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6883e08d0432d5a86aab150f0320a34e3c0af59","tid":2372068,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T10:56:55.000Z","msg":"黨媒跟住出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4768e1b9b4d9a35cd3a4a424892294c616015324","tid":2372068,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T11:32:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj